== 圣火传递 ==
[[File:2014_Asian_Games_opening_ceremony_3.jpg|thumb]]
2013年10月，火炬公布。仁川亚运会火炬上端内部为蓝色，象征着仁川的天空与大海，上下端外部为灰色，彰显一种坚实而稳定的气质。此外，用于火炬的辅助颜色有黄、红、绿、紫等，代表亚洲5个区域<ref>{{cite news|title=2014仁川亚运火炬 设计灵感源自仁川市鸟仙鹤|url=http://sports.163.com/14/0913/12/A6186GJ500051CAQ.html|accessdate=2014-09-13|newspaper=网易|date=2014-09-13|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405024745/http://sports.163.com/14/0913/12/A6186GJ500051CAQ.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年8月9日，亚运圣火采集仪式于[[印度|印度]][[新德里|新德里]][[德扬·昌德国家体育场|德扬·昌德国家体育场]]举行，是首次在东道国以外点燃火炬<ref>{{cite news|last=Sun-Hyoung|first=Kim|title=2014 AG Torch Designs Are Revealed|url=http://www.incheon2014ag.org/news/press/release/standard/view?menuId=3&bbsId=4663&cnId=6036&rows=28&pageNo=2&searchOpt=&searchTxt=|accessdate=27 March 2014|newspaper=IAGOC|date=14 October 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140417135816/http://www.incheon2014ag.org/news/press/release/standard/view?menuId=3&bbsId=4663&cnId=6036&rows=28&pageNo=2&searchOpt=&searchTxt=|archivedate=2014年4月17日}}</ref>。2014年8月12日，圣火于[[山东省|山东省]][[威海市|威海市]]传递<ref>{{cite news|title=仁川亚运圣火成功在威海传递 系中国唯一传递城市|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140813/41558147_0.shtml|accessdate=2014-09-13|newspaper=凤凰网|date=2014-08-13|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405024752/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140813/41558147_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而国内的采集仪式8月12日于[[江华岛|江华岛]][[摩尼山|摩尼山]]举行<ref>{{cite news|title=仁川亚运会圣火采集 韩国“仙女”盛装迎火种|url=http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20140812/41548029_0.shtml#p=1|accessdate=2014-09-13|newspaper=凤凰网|date=2014-08-12|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405024757/http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20140812/41548029_0.shtml#p=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本土的传递于2014年8月13日开始，途径70个城市，总长达5700公里<ref>{{cite news|last1=You|first1=Anna|title=The Torch of the Incheon Asian Games lights in New Delhi|url=http://www.incheon2014ag.org/news/press/release/standard/view?menuId=3&bbsId=4663&cnId=7792&rows=1&pageNo=1&searchOpt=&searchTxt=|accessdate=12 August 2014|work=IAGOC|publisher=Incheon2014ag.org|date=11 August 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140812135920/http://www.incheon2014ag.org/news/press/release/standard/view?menuId=3&bbsId=4663&cnId=7792&rows=1&pageNo=1&searchOpt=&searchTxt=|archivedate=2014年8月12日}}</ref>。亞運聖火2014年9月17日，抵達主辦城市南韓仁川市，展開最後一站的傳遞，電視劇[[朱蒙|朱蒙]]的主角[[宋一國|宋一國]]，以「前抱後背」攜3胞胎兒子傳遞聖火<ref>[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201409180124-1.aspx 亞運開幕前前夕 聖火仁川市傳遞] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201409180124-1.aspx |date=20160304201015 }}，中央社，2014年9月17日</ref>。

== 比賽 ==
===开幕式===
[[File:2014_Asian_Games_opening_ceremony_32.jpg|thumb]]
开幕式于当地时间9月19日晚7点19分举行（北京时间9月19日晚6点19分举行），文艺表演由电影导演[[林权泽|林权泽]]和剧作家兼演员[[张真|张真]]执导，艺人金成柱和KBS主持人云速英主持。出席开幕典礼的有[[韩国总统|韩国总统]][[朴槿惠|朴槿惠]]、[[国际奥委会|国际奥委会]]主席[[托马斯·巴赫|托马斯·巴赫]]、[[东京都知事|东京都知事]][[舛添要一|舛添要一]]和仁川市市长[[安相洙|安相洙]]<ref name="Japan Times">{{cite news|last1=Hueston|first1=Dave|title=Festive opening ceremony marks start of Asian Games|url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/sports/2014/09/19/more-sports/festive-opening-ceremony-marks-start-of-asian-games/#.VB2RBRY_n4s|accessdate=20 September 2014|agency=Kyodo|publisher=The Japan Times|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127075108/https://www.japantimes.co.jp/sports/2014/09/19/more-sports/festive-opening-ceremony-marks-start-of-asian-games/#.VB2RBRY_n4s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Asian Games Opening Ceremony: a showcase to Korea's past and future|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/asian-games-opening-ceremony-a-showcase-to-koreas-past-and-future/500182-5-23.html|accessdate=20 September 2014|publisher=IBN|archive-date=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008094048/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/asian-games-opening-ceremony-a-showcase-to-koreas-past-and-future/500182-5-23.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。文艺汇演在[[张东健|张东健]]和[[金秀贤|金秀贤]]的讲述下拉开大幕，被分为四幕：太古的亚洲、以海沟通的亚洲、亲如一家的亚洲和未来的亚洲，以数字影像展现韩国的过去和未来。演员包括中国钢琴家[[郎朗|郎朗]]、女高音歌唱家[[曹秀美|曹秀美]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Oinam|first1=Jayantam|title=2014 Incheon Asian Games: Opening Ceremony - As it happened...|url=http://zeenews.india.com/sports/2014-asian-games/india/2014-incheon-asian-games-opening-ceremony-as-it-happened_1472632.html|accessdate=20 September 2014|publisher=ZeeNews|date=19 September 2014|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210081013/https://zeenews.india.com/sports/2014-asian-games/india/2014-incheon-asian-games-opening-ceremony-as-it-happened_1472632.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和《[[江南Style|江南Style]]》原唱[[Psy|Psy]]<ref name="李英愛燃亞運聖火 騎馬舞超嗨">[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201409190452-1.aspx 李英愛燃亞運聖火 騎馬舞超嗨] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201409190452-1.aspx |date=20160304193448 }}，中央社，2014年9月19日</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Bodeen|first1=Christopher|title=Asian Games opening ceremony closes Gangnam Style|url=http://www.newstimes.com/sports/article/Asian-Games-prepares-for-opening-ceremony-5766227.php|accessdate=20 September 2014|publisher=Newstimes.com|date=19 September 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140920162008/http://www.newstimes.com/sports/article/Asian-Games-prepares-for-opening-ceremony-5766227.php|archivedate=2014年9月20日}}</ref>。女演员[[李英爱|李英爱]]偕同两位韩国少年，点燃主火炬<ref name="李英愛燃亞運聖火 騎馬舞超嗨"/><ref>{{cite news|last1=Jun|first1=Kwanwoo|title=Asian Games Opening Ceremony Torch Bearer Revealed Early|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/korearealtime/2014/09/19/asian-games-opening-ceremony-torch-bearer-revealed-early/|accessdate=20 September 2014|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=19 September 2014|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405024847/https://blogs.wsj.com/korearealtime/2014/09/19/asian-games-opening-ceremony-torch-bearer-revealed-early/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 闭幕式 ===
闭幕式于当地时间10月4日晚7点19分（北京时间10月4日晚6点19分）在[[仁川亚运会主体育场|仁川亚运会主体育场]]举行，由开幕式导演[[林权泽|林权泽]]和[[张真|张真]]执导，主题为：“我们仁川的宝贵回忆<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.gxnews.com.cn/staticpages/20140411/newgx5347d89f-10075656.shtml|title=仁川亚组委揭秘第17届亚运会|work=广西新闻网|date=2014-04-11|accessdate=2014-10-05|archive-date=2018-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927093919/http://news.gxnews.com.cn/staticpages/20140411/newgx5347d89f-10075656.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。仪式由三部分组成，第一部分为揭幕倒计时，第二部分以特殊的影像回顾赛事，最后一部分为祝贺性表演。众多壮观的表演融进盛大的闭幕式中。[[CN_Blue|CN Blue]]、[[BIGBANG|BIGBANG]]和[[Sistar|Sistar]]等一众韩流明星于最后一部分表演登场。随后，赛会旗帜移交给[[2018年亚洲运动会|下一届赛事]]主办国[[印尼|印尼]]的代表，最后火炬熄灭给闭幕式划上句号。[[亚奥理事会|亚奥理事会]]主席[[谢赫·艾哈迈德·法赫德·艾哈迈德·萨巴赫|谢赫·艾哈迈德·法赫德·艾哈迈德·萨巴赫]]在致辞中表示：“每个人都对赛事的成功和水平感到满意<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/asian-games-2014-closing-ceremony-live-17th-asiad-draws-to-a-close/503812-5-23.html |title=As it happened: Asian Games 2014 Closing Ceremony |accessdate=2014-10-05 |archive-date=2015-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103120737/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/asian-games-2014-closing-ceremony-live-17th-asiad-draws-to-a-close/503812-5-23.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

[[朝鲜劳动党|朝鲜劳动党]][[朝鲜劳动党中央书记局|中央书记局]]书记[[崔龙海|崔龙海]]和[[朝鲜国防委员会|朝鲜国防委员会]]副委员长[[黄炳瑞|黄炳瑞]]等朝鲜高层官员到场观看仪式，抵达韩国与韩国官员举行会谈。这是两国高层领导人五年来的首次面谈<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20141004/42138701_0.shtml|title=朝鲜将派高级代表团出席仁川亚运闭幕式 当晚返回|work=[[新华社|新华社]]|date=2014-10-04|accessdate=2014-10-05|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405024853/http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20141004/42138701_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

