==奖牌榜==
{{main|2014年亚洲运动会奖牌榜}}
{{:2014年亚洲运动会奖牌榜}}

== 比赛項目 ==
本屆亞運擬設有36個大項，437個小項。其中有28项[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会|下届奥运会]]的比赛项目，8项非奥运项目：[[棒球|棒球]]、[[保龄球|保龄球]]、[[板球|板球]]、[[卡巴迪|卡巴迪]]、[[空手道|空手道]]、[[藤球|藤球]]、[[壁球|壁球]]和[[武术|武术]]。项目名单最终于2010年12月9日在[[阿曼|阿曼]][[马斯喀特|马斯喀特]][[亚奥理事会|亚奥理事会]]执行委员会会议上确定<ref>{{cite news|title=Incheon 2014 issues delayed|url=http://www.ocasia.org/News/IndexNewsRM.aspx?redirect=1492|accessdate=2010-11-14|newspaper=Olympic Council of Asia|date=2010-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727140834/http://www.ocasia.org/News/IndexNewsRM.aspx?redirect=1492|archive-date=2011-07-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Incheon Asian Games to Feature 36 Sports|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/12/10/2010121000806.html|accessdate=2010-12-10|newspaper=The Chosun Ilbo|date=2010-12-10|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929194211/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/12/10/2010121000806.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。滑輪溜冰、棋类（[[围棋|围棋]]、[[象棋|象棋]]）、[[撞球|撞球]]、[[垒球|垒球]]、[[運動舞蹈|運動舞蹈]]和[[龙舟|龙舟]]这六项往届赛事项目被删<ref>{{cite news|title=Thirty-six sports to be competed at 2014 Incheon Asian Games|url=http://www.businessghana.com/portal/sports/news.php?op=getNews&id=19754&news_cat_id=3|accessdate=2010-12-10|newspaper=BusinessGhana|date=2010-12-09|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107090117/http://www.businessghana.com/portal/sports/news.php?op=getNews&id=19754&news_cat_id=3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年7月13日于[[东京|东京]]举办的第30届会议上，棒球与垒球合并为同一项目，[[软式网球|软式网球]]归于网球<ref>{{cite news|title=Official sports program approved at 58th OCA Executive Board meeting|url=http://eng.incheon2014ag.org/program/board/detail.jsp?menuID=002004001&boardTypeID=%20414&boardID=2255&mode=detail|accessdate=2011-07-14|newspaper=Incheon2014ag.org|date=2011-07-14|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608071735/http://eng.incheon2014ag.org/program/board/detail.jsp?menuID=002004001&boardTypeID=%20414&boardID=2255&mode=detail|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。复合射箭、[[铁人三项|铁人三项]]混合接力和[[柔道|团体柔道]]首次引入赛事<ref>{{cite news|first=S. Sabanayakan|title=Incheon Asian Games to include compound archery|url=http://www.thehindu.com/sport/other-sports/article2683861.ece|accessdate=2011-12-03|newspaper=The Hindu|date=2011-12-03|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413141448/http://www.thehindu.com/sport/other-sports/article2683861.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=仁川亚运会首枚金牌将诞生于射击女子10米气步枪|url=http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2014/04-12/6056752.shtml|accessdate=13 April 2014|newspaper=China News|date=12 April 2014|language=zh|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107105440/http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2014/04-12/6056752.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

亞運會的非奧運項目變更，受組織者討論的影響。有人建議將[[板球|板球]]從方案中移除，認為精通該項目的國家太少，缺乏該賽事的基礎設施。然而，亞奧理事會對擬取消板球的計畫表示異議，認為其日益普及，能引起觀眾的興趣<ref>{{cite news|last=K Samyal|first=Sanjjeev|title=India may face a gold drought at Incheon Asian Games 2014|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/sport/report_india-may-face-a-gold-drought-at-incheon-asian-games-2014_1467839|accessdate=2010-11-25|newspaper=Daily News & Analysis|date=2010-11-17|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025000107/http://www.dnaindia.com/sport/report_india-may-face-a-gold-drought-at-incheon-asian-games-2014_1467839|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
