== 争议 ==
{{main|2014年亞洲運動會相關問題}}
=== 朝鲜国旗被禁 ===
仁川亚运会组委会在仁川及周边多个城市街道悬挂[[朝鲜国旗|朝鲜国旗]]，引发韩国保守派人士不满。韩国政府已就朝鲜国旗在仁川亚运会期间使用范围作出规定，只允许朝鲜代表团在赛场、运动员村等部分场地使用朝鲜国旗，韩国民众在仁川亚运会期间不得持有朝鲜国旗或把它们带到比赛场地。一旦类似行为被认定违反《国家保安法》，相关人员将被移交司法部门处理<ref>{{cite news|title=韩国街道禁挂朝鲜国旗|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2014-09-13/143430845808.shtml|accessdate=2014-09-13|newspaper=新浪|date=2014-09-13|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329030249/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2014-09-13/143430845808.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== JYJ遭不公正对待 ===
赛事形象大使、韩国偶像组合[[JYJ|JYJ]]在开闭幕式上的表演据称被撤，移至开幕式暖场表演<ref>{{cite news|title=JYJ excluded from Incheon Asian Games opener|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/jyj-excluded-from-incheon-asian-games-opener/|accessdate=4 July 2014|publisher=ManilaBulletin|date=2 July 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714173812/http://www.mb.com.ph/jyj-excluded-from-incheon-asian-games-opener/|archivedate=2014年7月14日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=JYJ 측 공식입장 "인천AG 약속 지켜달라, 불공정 외압 아니길" [전문]|url=http://news.nate.com/view/20140701n30920|accessdate=2 July 2014|publisher=NATE|date=1 July 2014|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405025338/https://news.nate.com/view/20140701n30920|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他艺人，如[[Psy|Psy]]、[[BIGBANG|BIGBANG]]、[[CNBLUE|CNBLUE]]和[[EXO|EXO]]的表演不变<ref>{{cite news|title=싸이·빅뱅·JYJ·엑소, 2014인천AG 개폐막식 선다|url=http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=shm&sid1=106&oid=109&aid=0002817426|accessdate=4 July 2014|publisher=KoreaHerald|date=1 July 2014}}</ref>。消息曝光后，其粉丝要求组委会公平对待<ref>{{cite news|first1=Xiaolong|title=JYJ dropped from IAG opening and closing performances?|url=http://www.hellokpop.com/2014/07/04/jyj-dropped-from-iag-opening-and-closing-performances/|accessdate=6 July 2014|publisher=Hellokpop|date=4 July 2014|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405025347/https://www.hellokpop.com/2014/07/04/jyj-dropped-from-iag-opening-and-closing-performances/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终，组合将演唱赛会主题曲<ref>{{cite news|last1=Min-jin|first1=Kim|title=JYJ to perform at Incheon Asiad opening ceremony|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20140820000969|accessdate=21 August 2014|publisher=The Korea Herald|date=20 August 2014|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405025349/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20140820000969|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 比赛不名譽手段 ===
*[[2014年亞洲運動會自由車比賽|自行车]]方面，[[2014年亞洲運動會中國香港代表團|香港]]车手对取代奥运会和世锦赛常用的250米室内赛车场的333米户外赛车场表示关注。[[香港单车联会|香港单车联会]]表示，室外赛车场对现代自行车而言实属罕见，他们需要长途跋涉，到类似环境中实践<ref>{{cite news|title=Hong Kong raise alarm over Asian Games old-style cycling track|url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/hong-kong/article/1458744/hong-kong-raise-alarm-over-asian-games-old-style-cycling-track|accessdate=13 April 2014|newspaper=South China Morning Post|date=27 March 2014|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329030318/https://www.scmp.com/sport/hong-kong/article/1458744/hong-kong-raise-alarm-over-asian-games-old-style-cycling-track|dead-url=no}}</ref>。组委会否认这对主办国有任何好处，表示重新调整赛道，需经过[[国际自行车联盟|国际自行车联盟]]的批准<ref>{{cite news|last=Butler|first=Nick|title=Incheon 2014 unconcerned by criticism over track cycling venue at Asian Games|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/major-games/asian-games/1019226-incheon-2014-unconcerned-by-criticism-over-track-cycling-venue-at-asian-games|accessdate=13 April 2014|newspaper=inside the games|date=2 April 2014|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006090739/http://www.insidethegames.biz/major-games/asian-games/1019226-incheon-2014-unconcerned-by-criticism-over-track-cycling-venue-at-asian-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

*中华台北队的美籍篮球员[[戴维斯_(台湾)|昆西·戴维斯]]被取消参赛资格。组委会表示，戴维斯仅在新国家生活了两个月，少于非亚洲籍选手参赛所需的最少居住时间。韩国为给主队争取夺金优势而操纵规则的行为，受到指责<ref>[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201409030344-1.aspx 戴維斯不能打亞運 疑韓國作梗] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201409030344-1.aspx |date=20160304125146 }}，中央社，2014年9月3日</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Shan|first1=Shelley|title=US-born player no longer eligible for Asian Games|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/09/05/2003599061|accessdate=7 September 2014|publisher=Taipei Times|date=5 September 2014|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107104021/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/09/05/2003599061|dead-url=no}}</ref>。基于同样的原因，菲律宾[[归化|归化]]球员[[安德雷·布拉奇|安德雷·布拉奇]]被取消资格，尽管[[国际篮联|国际篮联]]宣称他有参赛资格。主办方给出球员必须于所在国家居住满三年或以上才能参赛的规则<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dy|first1=Adrian|title=Despite FIBA ruling, OCA rules Blatche ineligible for 2014 Asian Games|url=http://www.slamonlineph.com/despite-fiba-ruling-oca-rules-blatche-ineligible-2014-asian-games/|accessdate=8 September 2014|publisher=Slam Philippines|date=8 September 2014|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405025416/http://slamonlineph.com/despite-fiba-ruling-oca-rules-blatche-ineligible-2014-asian-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

*[[2014年亞洲運動會羽毛球比賽|羽球]]項目，[[2014年亞洲運動會韓國代表團|南韓]]運用其地主優勢，依地主選手賽事狀況調整[[空調|空調]]開關，影響比賽進行。<ref>{{cite news|title=南韓無所不「弄」？ 我羽球隊自備午餐|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/sports/breakingnews/1111734|accessdate=2014-09-21|publisher=自由時報|date=2014-09-21|archive-date=2014-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226005940/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/sports/breakingnews/1111734|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=場上吹神風？ 日選手控韓疑開空調暗助|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/sports/20140922/474349|accessdate=2014-09-22|publisher=蘋果日報|date=2014-09-22|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194416/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/sports/20140922/474349|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*[[2014年亞洲運動會棒球比賽|棒球]]項目，[[中華成棒隊|中华台北棒球代表队]]的[[羅嘉仁|羅嘉仁]]賽前無預警被通知藥檢（通過藥檢），無法至牛棚練球，和國際慣例的賽後檢查明顯不同。由於羅嘉仁是中華隊中唯一具有美國職棒大聯盟資歷的選手，這項突如其來且針對性相當明顯的舉動也被認為是地主手段之一。<ref>{{cite news|title=南韓又奧步？　羅嘉仁被抓去藥檢|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/sports/20140922/473921/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E5%8F%88%E5%A5%A7%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E7%BE%85%E5%98%89%E4%BB%81%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%93%E5%8E%BB%E8%97%A5%E6%AA%A2/|accessdate=2014-09-22|publisher=蘋果日報|date=2014-09-22|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155647/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/sports/20140922/473921/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E5%8F%88%E5%A5%A7%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E7%BE%85%E5%98%89%E4%BB%81%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%93%E5%8E%BB%E8%97%A5%E6%AA%A2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*印度輕量級女拳擊手戴維（Sarita Devi）因不公正的判決，拒領銅牌，同時於頒獎時將銅牌直接掛在因不公正判決獲勝銀牌的韓國選手朴志娜（Park Ji-Na）脖子上，引起仁川亞運主辦單位及[[國際拳擊總會|國際拳擊總會]]（AIBA）不滿。雖然戴維已經公開道歉，國際拳擊總會仍然執意要懲處戴維，此事件將成為運動賽事主辦單位及運動協會最不名譽的黑幕操作記錄<ref>{{cite news|first1=PTI|title=Mary Kom in final, Sarita Devi robbed of win at Asian Games|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2014-09-30/news/54475143_1_asian-games-l-sarita-devi-incheon|accessdate=2014-10-04|publisher=The Economic Times|date=2014-09-30|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305015824/http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2014-09-30/news/54475143_1_asian-games-l-sarita-devi-incheon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 兴奋剂检测 ===
比賽期間共有1600名運動員的1920件樣本被測試，6名運動員因興奮劑檢測結果呈陽性被停賽<ref name=doping>{{cite news|last1=Rutherford|first1=Peter|last2=Chakraborty|first2=Amlan|title=Games-China's hammer champion Zhang tests positive|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-2779263/Games-Chinese-hammer-gold-medallist-Zhang-tests-positive.html|accessdate=2014-10-03|agency=路透社|publisher=Mail Online|date=2014-10-03|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405025439/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-2779263/Games-Chinese-hammer-gold-medallist-Zhang-tests-positive.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

9月14日距比赛开幕还有五日，塔吉克斯坦足球运动员克赫许·别克纳扎罗夫（Khurshed Beknazarov）因[[甲基丙烯酰胺|甲基丙烯酰胺]]检测结果呈阳性，被暂停所有足球活动30天<ref>{{cite news|title=AFC suspends Tajikistan footballer for doping at Asiad|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/sports-news/asiangames2014/afc-suspends-tajikistan-footballer-for-doping-at-asiad/article1-1268093.aspx|accessdate=2014-09-25|publisher=hindustan times|date=2014-09-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925041458/http://www.hindustantimes.com/sports-news/asiangames2014/afc-suspends-tajikistan-footballer-for-doping-at-asiad/article1-1268093.aspx|archivedate=2014-09-25}}</ref>。9月25日，柬埔寨软式网球运动员易·苏芬汗（Yi Sophny）[[西布曲明|西布曲明]]检测呈阳性<ref>{{cite news|title=Cambodian athlete expelled for doping at Asian Games|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/sports/article/cambodian-athlete-expelled-for-doping-at-asian-games|accessdate=2014-09-25|publisher=Malaysian Insider|date=2014-09-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925223550/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/sports/article/cambodian-athlete-expelled-for-doping-at-asian-games|archivedate=2014-09-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Two more athletes fail doping tests at Asian Games|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/sports-news/asiangames2014/two-more-athletes-fail-doping-tests-at-asian-games/article1-1268094.aspx|accessdate=2014-09-25|publisher=hindustan times|date=2014-09-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925074931/http://www.hindustantimes.com/sports-news/asiangames2014/two-more-athletes-fail-doping-tests-at-asian-games/article1-1268094.aspx|archivedate=2014-09-25}}</ref>。9月30日，马来西亚武术金牌得主戴巧玄（Tai Cheau Xuen）[[西布曲明|西布曲明]]检测亦为阳性，其金牌被剥夺<ref>{{cite news|title=Malaysian gold medalist kicked out of Asian Games for doping (updated)|url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/xinhua-news-agency/140930/malaysian-gold-medalist-kicked-out-asian-games-doping-update|accessdate=2014-09-30|agency=新华社|publisher=globalpost|date=2014-09-30|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006205943/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/xinhua-news-agency/140930/malaysian-gold-medalist-kicked-out-asian-games-doping-update|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马来西亚官员不服取消比赛的判决，向体育仲裁法庭申诉却被驳回<ref>{{cite news|title=Malaysia to appeal gold medalist expulsion - Khairy|url=http://english.astroawani.com/news/show/malaysia-to-appeal-gold-medalist-expulsion-khairy-45060|accessdate=2014-09-30|publisher=Astro Awani|date=2014-09-30|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111164208/http://english.astroawani.com/news/show/malaysia-to-appeal-gold-medalist-expulsion-khairy-45060|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Malaysia lose appeal against doping failure|url=https://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/25173198/malaysia-lose-appeal-against-doping-failure/|accessdate=2014-10-03|agency=AFP|publisher=Yahoo! 7 News|date=2014-10-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006160204/https://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/25173198/malaysia-lose-appeal-against-doping-failure/|archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref>。同一天，伊拉克举重运动员穆罕默德·埃弗里（Mohammed al Aifuri）[[本胆烷醇酮|本胆烷醇酮]]和[[雄甾酮|雄甾酮]]检测呈阳性，是他六年来第二个不合格的药检<ref>{{cite news|title=Asian Games 2014: Weightlifter from Iraq caught doping|url=http://www.cricketcountry.com/asian-games-2014/asian-games-2014-weightlifter-from-iraq-caught-doping-194010|accessdate=2014-09-30|publisher=The Cricket Country|date=2014-09-30|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405025530/https://www.cricketcountry.com/asian-games-2014/asian-games-2014-weightlifter-from-iraq-caught-doping-194010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年他曾因服用[[去氢甲睾酮|去氢甲睾酮]]而被禁赛的他，这一次，将面临[[国际举重联合会|国际举重联合会]]的禁令<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi weightlifter caught doping at Asiad|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/tournaments/asian-games-2014/news/Iraqi-weightlifter-caught-doping-at-Asiad/articleshow/43909834.cms|accessdate=2014-10-03|publisher=The Times of India|date=2014-09-30|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121111317/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/tournaments/asian-games-2014/news/Iraqi-weightlifter-caught-doping-at-Asiad/articleshow/43909834.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月1日，叙利亚空手道选手努尔·亚丁-库尔迪（Nour-Aldin al-Kurdi）[[克伦特罗|克伦特罗]]（俗称[[瘦肉精|瘦肉精]]）检测呈阳性<ref>{{cite news|last1=France-Presse|first1=Agence|title=Track, Medal, Doping Rows Cloud Asian Games|url=http://sports.ndtv.com/asian-games-2014/news/230756-track-medal-doping-rows-cloud-asian-games|accessdate=2014-10-03|publisher=NDTV Sports|date=2014-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006141302/http://sports.ndtv.com/asian-games-2014/news/230756-track-medal-doping-rows-cloud-asian-games|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。10月3日，中国链球运动员[[张文秀|张文秀]]第二枚金牌因[[玉米赤霉醇|玉米赤霉醇]]检测呈阳性而被剥夺<ref>{{cite news|title=中国选手张文秀掉进“药罐”|url=http://xmwb.news365.com.cn/tyxw/201410/t20141004_1335930.html|work=[[新民晚报|新民晚报]]|date=2014年10月3日|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141004144732/http://xmwb.news365.com.cn/tyxw/201410/t20141004_1335930.html|archivedate=2014年10月4日|accessdate=2014年10月4日}}</ref>。

2015年5月27日，[[亞洲奧林匹克委員會|亞洲奧林匹克委員會]]宣佈南韓游泳運動員[[朴泰桓|朴泰桓]]在仁川亞運前夕所接受的興奮劑檢測之結果呈陽性，他體內被檢測出含有某種增加肌肉強度的睪丸素，因此[[亞洲奧林匹克委員會|亞洲奧會]]決定收回朴泰桓在仁川亞運奪得的獎牌、獎狀和獎金<ref>{{cite news|title=朴泰桓違禁 亞奧會收回仁川亞運獎牌|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%B4%E6%B3%B0%E6%A1%93%E9%81%95%E7%A6%81-%E4%BA%9E%E5%A5%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E4%BB%81%E5%B7%9D%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E7%8D%8E%E7%89%8C-075242121.html|work=[[中央社|中央社]]|date=2015年5月28日|accessdate=2015年5月28日|archive-date=2020年3月29日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329030459/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%B4%E6%B3%B0%E6%A1%93%E9%81%95%E7%A6%81-%E4%BA%9E%E5%A5%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E4%BB%81%E5%B7%9D%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E7%8D%8E%E7%89%8C-075242121.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 圣火熄滅 ===
聖火於9月20日晚曾因故障而熄滅，12分鐘後重新點燃。<ref>{{cite news|title=仁川亚运会主火炬发生故障 圣火熄灭12分钟后重燃|url=http://sports.people.com.cn/n/2014/0921/c22176-25702635.html|work=人民网|date=2014-09-21|accessdate=2015-06-28|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329030507/http://sports.people.com.cn/n/2014/0921/c22176-25702635.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

